title: GET UP AND MAKE IT HAPPEN
itunes:title: GET UP AND MAKE IT HAPPEN
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
GET UP AND MAKE IT HAPPEN! Don't just sit there, waiting for the world to give you the golden ticket. GET UP and Go GET IT! You were created to do great things, it's time to reap the rewards! One of the best motivational speech compilations featuring Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity), Billy Alsbrooks (https://bit.ly/BillyAlsbrooksMotiversity), Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity), Jessica Houston (https://bit.ly/DrJessicaHoustonMotiversity) and Freddy Fri (https://bit.ly/FreddyFriMotiversity).


Music by Secession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube), Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/), and Whitesand (https://www.youtube.com/c/WhitesandComposer).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
